Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to look for it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.42,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前に探した記憶を辿れば　多分
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to find it by tracing my memory.
