Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.41,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなものとか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:28.87,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは何
