Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bride? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.94,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,花嫁　私が
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose bride will I become?
